Sentencas: Subsolidus equilibria in air in the RuO2-PbO-CeO2 systems were studied with the aim of obtaining information on possible interactions between the Pb2Ru2O6.5 based cathode and CeO2 based solid electrolyte in solid oxide fuel cells (SOFC).
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the RuO2-PbO-CeO2 system

Sentencas: No ternary compound was found in the system.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the RuO2-PbO-CeO2 system

Sentencas: The tie line is between Pb2Ru2O6.5 and CeO2.
Titulo: Subsolidus phase equilibria in the RuO2-PbO-CeO2 system

Sentencas: The obtained results indicate that a Pb2Ru2O6.5-based cathode material would not react with a ceria based solid electrolyte in a SOFC.
